    "description": "Need help? Want access to this workflow + many more paid workflows + live Q&A sessions with a top verified n8n creator?\n\n[Join the community](https://www.skool.com/beyond-nodes-automation-lab-2006/about)\n\nComplete MCP server exposing all SecurityScorecard Tool operations to AI agents. Zero configuration needed - all 19 operations pre-built.\n\n## ‚ö° Quick Setup\n\n1. **Import** this workflow into your n8n instance\n2. **Activate** the workflow to start your MCP server\n3. **Copy** the webhook URL from the MCP trigger node\n4. **Connect** AI agents using the MCP URL\n\n## üîß How it Works\n\n‚Ä¢ **MCP Trigger**: Serves as your server endpoint for AI agent requests\n‚Ä¢ **Tool Nodes**: Pre-configured for every SecurityScorecard Tool operation\n‚Ä¢ **AI Expressions**: Automatically populate parameters via `$fromAI()` placeholders\n‚Ä¢ **Native Integration**: Uses official n8n SecurityScorecard Tool tool with full error handling\n\n## üìã Available Operations (19 total)\n\nEvery possible SecurityScorecard Tool operation is included:\n\n### üîß Company (5 operations)\n\n‚Ä¢ **Get a company factor scores and issue counts**\n‚Ä¢ **Get a company's historical factor scores**\n‚Ä¢ **Get a company's historical scores**\n‚Ä¢ **Get company information and a summary of their scorecard**\n‚Ä¢ **Get a company's score improvement plan**\n\n### üîß Industry (3 operations)\n\n‚Ä¢ **Get factor scores for an industry**\n‚Ä¢ **Get historical factor scores for an industry**\n‚Ä¢ **Get the score for an industry**\n\n### üîß Invite (1 operations)\n\n‚Ä¢ **Create an invite**\n\n### üîß Portfolio (4 operations)\n\n‚Ä¢ **Create a portfolio**\n‚Ä¢ **Delete a portfolio**\n‚Ä¢ **Get many portfolios**\n‚Ä¢ **Update a portfolio**\n\n### üîß Portfoliocompany (3 operations)\n\n‚Ä¢ **Add a portfolio company**\n‚Ä¢ **Get many portfolio companies**\n‚Ä¢ **Remove a portfolio company**\n\n### üîß Report (3 operations)\n\n‚Ä¢ **Download a report**\n‚Ä¢ **Generate a report**\n‚Ä¢ **Get many reports**\n\n## ü§ñ AI Integration\n\n**Parameter Handling**: AI agents automatically provide values for:\n‚Ä¢ Resource IDs and identifiers\n‚Ä¢ Search queries and filters\n‚Ä¢ Content and data payloads\n‚Ä¢ Configuration options\n\n**Response Format**: Native SecurityScorecard Tool API responses with full data structure\n\n**Error Handling**: Built-in n8n error management and retry logic\n\n## üí° Usage Examples\n\nConnect this MCP server to any AI agent or workflow:\n\n‚Ä¢ **Claude Desktop**: Add MCP server URL to configuration\n‚Ä¢ **Custom AI Apps**: Use MCP URL as tool endpoint\n‚Ä¢ **Other n8n Workflows**: Call MCP tools from any workflow\n‚Ä¢ **API Integration**: Direct HTTP calls to MCP endpoints\n\n## ‚ú® Benefits\n\n‚Ä¢ **Complete Coverage**: Every SecurityScorecard Tool operation available\n‚Ä¢ **Zero Setup**: No parameter mapping or configuration needed\n‚Ä¢ **AI-Ready**: Built-in `$fromAI()` expressions for all parameters\n‚Ä¢ **Production Ready**: Native n8n error handling and logging\n‚Ä¢ **Extensible**: Easily modify or add custom logic\n\n&gt; üÜì **[Free for community use](https://github.com/Cfomodz/community-use)!** Ready to deploy in under 2 minutes.",
